What:		/sys/bus/platform/devices/INOU0000:XX/water_cooler/wc_fan_mode
Date:		April 2026
KernelVersion:	7.3
Contact:	Erhan Bilgili <nano.matters.code@gmail.com>
Description:
		Returns the current water cooler fan control mode as an unsigned integer.

What:		/sys/bus/platform/devices/INOU0000:XX/ctgp_offset_max
Date:		April 2026
KernelVersion:	7.3
Contact:	Erhan Bilgili <nano.matters.code@gmail.com>
Description:
		Returns the maximum allowed configurable TGP (cTGP) offset in watts for this
		device, as reported by the ACPI SMRW firmware table. This limits the value that
		can be written to ctgp_offset.

		This attribute is only available on devices with NVIDIA cTGP control support and
		a valid SMRW table entry.

What:		/sys/bus/platform/devices/INOU0000:XX/db_offset_max
Date:		April 2026
KernelVersion:	7.3
Contact:	Erhan Bilgili <nano.matters.code@gmail.com>
Description:
		Returns the maximum allowed NVIDIA Dynamic Boost offset in watts for this device,
		as reported by the ACPI SMRW firmware table.

		This attribute is only available on devices with NVIDIA cTGP control support and
		a valid SMRW table entry.

What:		/sys/bus/platform/devices/INOU0000:XX/tgp_base
Date:		April 2026
KernelVersion:	7.3
Contact:	Erhan Bilgili <nano.matters.code@gmail.com>
Description:
		Returns the base Total Graphics Power (TGP) of the discrete GPU in watts, as
		reported by the ACPI SMRW firmware table.

		This attribute is only available on devices with NVIDIA cTGP control support and
		a valid SMRW table entry.

What:		/sys/bus/platform/devices/INOU0000:XX/vrm_current_limit
Date:		April 2026
KernelVersion:	7.3
