What:		/sys/bus/platform/devices/INOU0000:XX/fan_switch_speed
Date:		April 2026
KernelVersion:	7.3
Contact:	Erhan Bilgili <nano.matters.code@gmail.com>
Description:
		Controls the delay before fans ramp up to a new speed, in milliseconds.
		Writing "0" disables the delay. Non-zero values are rounded to the nearest 100ms
		and clamped to the range 100-12700ms.

		Reading this file returns the current delay in milliseconds, or "0" if the
		feature is disabled.
